### Authentication (SCRAM-SHA-256)
```rust
impl PgConnection {
    async fn authenticate_scram(&mut self, password: &str) -> Outcome<(), PgError> {
        // 1. Receive AuthenticationSASL
        // 2. Send SASLInitialResponse (client-first-message)
        // 3. Receive AuthenticationSASLContinue (server-first-message)
        // 4. Compute salted password, client key, stored key
